&lt;li&gt;A motivated strategist who enjoys collaborating across teams and departments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A customer-focused problem-solver who enjoys supporting clients from negotiation through implementation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An effective presenter and communicators&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A self-directed multitasker with excellent organizational skills&lt;/li&gt;
